zim-tools
------------------------------------------
Various ZIM command line tools.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.6-1
  file-5.46-1
  libdocopt0-0.6.3-1bl2
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libgumbo2-0.12.3-1bl1
  libicu76-76.1-2
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  libzim9-9.4.1-1bl1
  zlib0-1.3.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  Mustache-4.1-1bl2
  binutils-2.45.1-1
  cygport-0.37.6-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libdocopt-devel-0.6.3-1bl2
  libgtest-devel-1.17.0-1bl1
  libgumbo-devel-0.12.3-1bl1
  libicu-devel-76.1-2
  libzim-devel-9.4.1-1bl1
  meson-1.5.2-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1
  zlib-devel-1.3.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/openzim/zim-tools

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/openzim/zim-tools/archive/refs/tags/3.6.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack zim-tools-3.6.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./zim-tools-3.6.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/zim-tools-3.6.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/zim-tools-3.6.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(zim-tools)
  /usr/bin/zimbench.exe
  /usr/bin/zimcheck.exe
  /usr/bin/zimdiff.exe
  /usr/bin/zimdump.exe
  /usr/bin/zimpatch.exe
  /usr/bin/zimrecreate.exe
  /usr/bin/zimsearch.exe
  /usr/bin/zimsplit.exe
  /usr/bin/zimwriterfs.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/zim-tools.README
  /usr/share/doc/zim-tools/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/zim-tools/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/zim-tools/README.md

